pageContext.claim: “Did you hear the latest con job? President Obama is now trying to take credit for the Economic Boom taking place under the Trump Administration. He had the WEAKEST recovery since the Great Depression, despite Zero Fed Rate & MASSIVE quantitative easing. NOW, best jobs numbers.... ....ever.”
pageContext.analysis: Obama is not trying to take credit. Trump inherited a growing economy and declining unemployment from his predecessor, and that growth has continued largely at the same pace. The unemployment rate has not reached record lows under Trump.
